{"tid":1141394,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子會不會叫 ? 是會的....","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T04:22:36.000Z","uid":197098,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d6fa7b717eb7e2d03906396eaae4606c1d736d","tid":1141394,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"開心時會「<span style=\"color: red;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=13a970bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predatory animals)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。 <br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸: <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=7fdfd592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"},{"pid":"e63fc16e873a97c0491f2f904915aefb77113190","tid":1141394,"uid":132326,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"兔肉好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432953857e92edf415bebd49e069a40fead75ff4","tid":1141394,"uid":240396,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e63fc16e873a97c0491f2f904915aefb77113190","tid":1141394,"uid":132326,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"兔肉好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"識野<img src=\"/assets/faces